                You have better things to build
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-body-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Join hundreds of teams who trust Hook0 for reliable, secure webhook delivery. Get started in minutes.
            </p>

            <!-- Documentation Quick Links -->
            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
                <a href="https://documentation.hook0.com/tutorials/webhook-authentication" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm text-gray-300 hover:bg-white/10 hover:text-white transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path></svg>
                    Authentication
